on to my impressions of the products:
I LOVE the moisturizer- lightweight, hydrating and calming- checks all the boxes for me. I've used it SOOO much since the day i got  it cause it is so comfy on the skin and doesn't make the skin feel heavy at all. The face wash is an absolute dream cause of the texture- feels like a luxurious face wash for sure and as you can see from the video, my skin was still so plump and hydrated and clean post wash!

latestIgtvVideos.title: A very Affordable Morning Skincare Routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
SNP is affordability & inclusivity defined. 
The SNP Prep Range has the most simple yet effective ingredients list for beginners with skincare and I know quite a lot of you here are new to skincare. 
SNP is also sooooo affordable, I mean the Peptaronic range (pink) costs 750 bucks for such big bottles! They will last you a while. 
The whole range is suitable for ALL skin types and if you also use other actives, these will compliment them better, especially the SNP Peptaronic range 
They also have a cicaronic range which is for sensitive skin which i've not used here but i can assure y'all it will also be worth a try. 
I 11/10 recommend the whole range! 
Remember to use code GLOSS10 for 10% off* affiliated
